title: Zobrist describes Royals' patient approach
text: Zobrist describes Royals' patient approach OCT 12, 8:07 pm Second baseman Ben Zobrist says the Royals' eighth-inning rally started innocently enough with a bunch of singles, and "things just kind of steamrolled a little bit."
